Package org.apache.flex.swf.tags

This package contains classes and interfaces representing tags in a SWF file.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IAlwaysLongTag
    The ITags implements IAlwaysLongTag will always be serialized into a SWF tag with long header definition, regardless of the actual bytes used.
    ICharacterReferrer
    A SWF tag can refer to one or more SWF tag(s) by the character ID.
    ICharacterTag
    A character tag has Character ID.
    IDefineBinaryImageTag
    Interface for all binary data tags that represent an image.
    IDefineFontTag
    Common interface between DefineFontTag, DefineFontTag2, DefineFontTag3, DefineFontTag4.
    IFontInfo  
    IManagedTag
    A "managed" SWF tag cannot be added to SWFFrame pragmatically.
    ITag
    The interface for all the SWF tags.

Package org.apache.flex.swf.tags Description

This package contains classes and interfaces representing tags in a SWF file.

See the SWF File Format Specification for more information.
